OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry: What is it and why is
OL,4,Cit coming to the UK now?
OL,6,FUnder the cover of night, the Bayeux
OL,7,FTapestry arrived in the UK on Friday.
OL,9,FIt is the first time the almost 1,000-
OL,10,Fyear-old artifact is in the UK and
OL,11,Fhundreds of thousands of people have
OL,12,Falready bought the first batch of
OL,13,Ftickets to see it.
OL,15,FBut why is it in England, and how can
OL,16,Fyou get an opportunity to see it?
OL,18,FA brief history: What is the
OL,19,Ftapestry's cultural significance in
OL,20,FBritain and why is it here?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
