OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry: What is it and why is
OL,4,Cit coming to the UK now?
OL,6,FSince this week, the tapestry has been
OL,7,Fkept at the Bayeux Tapestry Museum in
OL,8,FFrance, where it has been on display
OL,9,Ffor 43 years. However, the museum is
OL,10,Fnow closed for renovation.
OL,12,FThe important piece of French and
OL,13,FBritish history is on loan in London
OL,14,Ffor the first time, being housed at
OL,15,Fthe British Museum.
OL,17,FHow popular is the exhibition expected
OL,18,Fto be?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
