OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry: What is it and why is
OL,4,Cit coming to the UK now?
OL,6,FWhen general admission tickets went on
OL,7,Fsale last week, the British Museum
OL,8,Frecorded the single biggest day of
OL,9,Fticket sales in its history,
OL,10,Fgenerating more than #2.4 million in
OL,11,Fsales in the first 24 hours.
OL,13,FAbout 100,000 tickets were sold on
OL,14,Ftheir first day on sale this month,
OL,15,Fand the museum anticipates that 7.5
OL,16,Fmillion people will visit the 11th-
OL,17,Fcentury artwork in London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
