OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783716522
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry: What is it and why is
OL,4,Cit coming to the UK now?
OL,6,FAround the excitement, however, the
OL,7,Fmove has not been without controversy.
OL,8,FSome restorers have expressed concerns
OL,9,Faround the safety of moving such a
OL,10,Fdelicate artifact.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, almost 70,000 people in
OL,13,FFrance reportedly signed a petition
OL,14,Fsaying the loan is a "cultural crime".
OL,16,FHow long is it on loan for, and how
OL,17,Fcan I see it?
OL,19,FThe tapestry will be open to the
OL,20,Fpublic from September 10 until July
OL,21,F2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
