OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry: What is it and why is
OL,4,Cit coming to the UK now?
OL,6,FOver the coming weeks, the artwork
OL,7,Fwill undergo condition checks before
OL,8,Fbeing carefully installed within a
OL,9,Fcustom showcase.
OL,11,FTickets have to be booked in advance,
OL,12,Fand are currently sold out on the
OL,13,FBritish Museum's website, but this
OL,14,Fdoesn't mean you have missed your
OL,15,Fopportunity.
OL,17,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
