OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1783716522
OL,3,CBayeux Tapestry: What is it and why is
OL,4,Cit coming to the UK now?
OL,6,FThe museum announced that there will
OL,7,Fbe two further ticket releases in
OL,8,FOctober and January.
OL,10,FTickets are currently priced at #33
OL,11,Ffor adults, free for under 16s, and at
OL,12,Freduced prices for students and
OL,13,Fdisabled visitors - according to their
OL,14,Fwebsite,
OL,16,FThey are also advertising members'
OL,17,Ftickets, with two further priority
OL,18,Fbooking windows for members who pay an
OL,19,Fannual membership fee of #82 a year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
